            <thetext>After resolving all config includes, the list of all available jobs is settled. 
After that, the jobs to run are expanded. The &quot;extend&quot; and &quot;run&quot; keys are the 
first to be resolved in any particular job. Only after that, macros are 
expanded within the job definition. This prohibits using macros in &quot;extend&quot; and 
&quot;run&quot; keys, which limits the possibility to parameterize these keys.

The generator should make a &quot;best effort&quot; to resolve macros in these keys, 
using the let bindings that are available so far.</thetext>
          </long_desc>
